# pyrst build outputs — `pyrst build <file.pyrs>` always emits its binary
# into the CURRENT directory named after the source basename (ignores -o
# and subdirectories), so tests/smoke_repl.pyrs builds to ./smoke_repl too.
# Regenerable; never commit these.
/main
/smoke_repl
/test_engine
/test_persist
/test_edge_cases
*.db
*.pdb
